abstracts.cdata!:
The Second Highway Project will include:
            (a) pavement strengthening of six sections of road,
            totalling 110 km; (b) a four-year program for improving
            highway maintenance through (i) the reorganization of
            maintenance operations and equipment repair, including staff
            training and (ii) the purchase of highway maintenance,
            workshop and radio equipment, spare parts, and weighbridges;
            and (c) preinvestment studies.
